name: Murder Drones
description: Murder Drones is a Youtube-based web series created by Glitch Productions which released in 2021. It's set in a post-apocaliptic exoplanet where all humans used to live before they accidentally exploded the planet's core. Now, it's habited by robots named Worker Drones. However, after they started gaining sentience, a new type of robots, Disassembly Drones, were sent with one objective: to eliminate every Worker Drone. Now, the Worker Drones all live inside a bunker underneath ice, hidden away from any Disassembly Drones.
